answer:
Please speak with your health care provider for interpretation of blood test results and need for any vaccine(s). In BC, if your birth date is on or after January 1, 1957 and you are not immune to rubella, you need documentation of 1 dose of live rubella vaccine given as the measles, mumps, rubella (MMR) vaccine.
Immunization Nurse
